  "content": "<p data-pid=\"5l61iHy_\">这场达特茅斯-普林斯顿的比赛给我们带来一个启示：我们的大部分推理过程实际上是在事后合理化——我们编造故事，让自己当前的观点显得更加连贯和有道理，但这并不一定能提高观点的准确性。<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//www.readthesequences.com/Against-Rationalization-Sequence\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">《反对合理化》</a>系列探讨了这一问题，而<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//www.readthesequences.com/Against-Doublethink-Sequence\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">《对抗双重思想》</a>（关于自我欺骗）和<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//www.readthesequences.com/Seeing-With-Fresh-Eyes-Sequence\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">《用新眼光看问题》</a>（关于挑战我们识别与预期和假设不符的证据的能力）系列则对此进行了进一步阐述。</p><p data-pid=\"1Q0pzF74\">——<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//www.readthesequences.com/Rationality-An-Introduction\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">《理性：序言》</a><sup data-text=\"理性：序言\" data-url=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/827867654\" data-draft-node=\"inline\" data-draft-type=\"reference\" data-numero=\"1\">[1]</sup>by Rob Bensinger</p><hr/><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/8246788669\" data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" data-image=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-873ecdcd65dde2e1f16891677abf0be2_qhd.jpg\" data-image-width=\"5472\" data-image-height=\"3648\" class=\"internal\">Thoughts Memo：了解偏见可能反而有害</a><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/12593770040\" data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" data-image=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/v2-f16154e462cbc26c412d0d86572ddec0_qhd.jpg\" data-image-width=\"6240\" data-image-height=\"4160\" class=\"internal\">Thoughts Memo：逐步自我更新</a><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/12852320444\" data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" data-image=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-d70588c5cecd27bd0a7fdb0eb62dcce0_l.jpg\" data-image-width=\"1024\" data-image-height=\"1024\" class=\"internal\">Thoughts Memo：以一当千的论证谬误</a><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/13265385885\" data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" data-image=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-1efa9d935aef83dce2e8e809a4a0e989_qhd.jpg\" data-image-width=\"6000\" data-image-height=\"4000\" class=\"internal\">Thoughts Memo：结论从何而来</a><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/15300705897\" data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" data-image=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-db1516149e617d9ff143a15423233b22_qhd.jpg\" data-image-width=\"6000\" data-image-height=\"4000\" class=\"internal\">Thoughts Memo：什么是证据筛选？</a><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/15807962622\" data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" data-image=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-49a182753963b1fad90ba797b5032b39_qhd.jpg\" data-image-width=\"2000\" data-image-height=\"1375\" class=\"internal\">Thoughts Memo：合理化</a><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/19114455919\" data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" data-image=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-dcd915edb68d9b76f8b25b8f5a2f57b9_qhd.jpg\" data-image-width=\"4256\" data-image-height=\"2832\" class=\"internal\">Thoughts Memo：理性的论证</a><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/23207691441\" data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" data-image=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-02b09c3cb588f3973c748671f5f2fca0_qhd.jpg\" data-image-width=\"2592\" data-image-height=\"1944\" class=\"internal\">Thoughts Memo：规避你信念中的真正弱点</a><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/25143636684\" data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" data-image=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-fbdb4d24d7e23ed91e29ade9c9c8e8db_qhd.jpg\" data-image-width=\"5961\" data-image-height=\"3353\" class=\"internal\">Thoughts Memo：动机性停止和动机性继续</a><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/26272313205\" data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" data-image=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-7ed6856317a56dd90d9c1db0163deef5_qhd.jpg\" data-image-width=\"4608\" data-image-height=\"3456\" class=\"internal\">Thoughts Memo：虚假辩白</a><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/26963337091\" data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" data-image=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-8118364be2133e778ff6d4471dca65c1_qhd.jpg\" data-image-width=\"4528\" data-image-height=\"3019\" class=\"internal\">Thoughts Memo：那是你拒绝的真正原因吗？</a><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/28043168145\" data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" data-image=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-142522f206107aa2c729a1fd9a49b761_qhd.jpg\" data-image-width=\"7952\" data-image-height=\"5304\" class=\"internal\">Thoughts Memo：关联的真理，传染的谎言</a><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/28295021724\" data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" data-image=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-cef3acd39d5f0440e88ebf86cab53d92_qhd.jpg\" data-image-width=\"275\" data-image-height=\"183\" class=\"internal\">Thoughts Memo：关于谎言和黑天鹅事件</a><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/30421407549\" data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" data-image=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-f16645451567ca6b53714a55dc45d83c_qhd.jpg\" data-image-width=\"4000\" data-image-height=\"3000\" class=\"internal\">Thoughts Memo：黑暗面的认识论</a><hr/><p data-pid=\"QnYCOA_Y\">上一篇：</p><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/7772409181\" data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" data-image=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-6bfdd556193421d9851cac348aee4d9d_qhd.jpg\" data-image-width=\"5184\" data-image-height=\"3456\" class=\"internal\">Thoughts Memo：人类恶行与混乱思维</a><p data-pid=\"P9h_AICo\">下一篇：</p><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/8246788669\" data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" data-image=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-873ecdcd65dde2e1f16891677abf0be2_qhd.jpg\" data-image-width=\"5472\" data-image-height=\"3648\" class=\"internal\">Thoughts Memo：了解偏见可能反而有害</a><hr/><blockquote data-pid=\"q6-pHLep\"><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//paratranz.cn/projects/3131\" class=\" wrap external\